metadata.name: TORIX #1
metadata.description:
TORIX, with 9,999 special NFT collections.

TORIX works as an objet that combines everything across reality and virtual world and can be formed into anything in the world.

TORIX is divided into a variety of parts including rare items, and among the 9,999 TORIXs, there are 99 special unique types.

TORIX holders are able to get the opportunity to directly participate in various platform services that expand to P2E, artist collaboration, digital figures, and metaverse.
